French financial group MetrologieInternational said it is issuing 73.8 mln francs worth of stockoption bonds with Banque Paribas as lead manager.    The eight-year issue at par will carry interest of six pctpayable on August 3. Existing shareholders will have prioritysubscription to the 1,000 franc nominal bonds on the basis ofone bond for 14 shares held.    Each bond will be accompanied by two warrants giving theright to subscribe to one 40 franc nominal share at a price of580 francs. REUTER&#3;